tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE customer_engagement_reports (
    report_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_id INT,
    channel VARCHAR(50),
    engagement_score FLOAT,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    completed BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE EngagementChannels (
    channel_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    channel_name TEXT,
    customer_id INT,
    engagement_date TIMESTAMP,
    engagement_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Customer (customer_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 customer_name VARCHAR(255),
 email VARCHAR(255),
 phone_number VARCHAR(15),
 sign_up_date TIMESTAMP)

CREATE TABLE Channel (channel_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 channel_name VARCHAR(255),
 channel_type VARCHAR(50),
 description TEXT)

CREATE TABLE Interaction (interaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 customer_id UUID,
 channel_id UUID,
 interaction_date TIMESTAMP,
 interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
 duration_seconds INT,
 FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id),
 FOREIGN KEY (channel_id) REFERENCES Channel(channel_id))

CREATE TABLE Report (report_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
 report_date TIMESTAMP,
 customer_id UUID,
 channel_id UUID,
 engagement_score FLOAT,
 report_details JSON,
 FOREIGN KEY (customer_id) REFERENCES Customer(customer_id),
 FOREIGN KEY (channel_id) REFERENCES Channel(channel_id))
